{"tid":2438958,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「女股神」Cathie Wood 牛市變得更廣闊 長遠有利旗下投資","createTime":"2021-03-09T01:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T04:08:04.000Z","uid":237459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f1f084c047095bf73bb60df2b062b7d700f701ec","tid":2438958,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T01:41:37.000Z","msg":"被視為「女股神」的美國方舟投管理創辦人兼行政總裁Cathie Wood接受《CNBC》訪問時表示，不擔心旗下基金近期下跌，並指牛市正變得更廣闊，包括價值投資策略。<br />\n<br />\n她認為目前牛市變得更強大，長遠有利公司的投資，又指近期股價下跌提供巨大機會，對投資組合內的股份變得更具信心。她表示，牛市規模變大並包含價值及更周期性行業，是對公司投資策略的好消息。最壞情況反而是另一次科技及電訊泡沬下，投資者只集中少數股份。<br />\n<br />\n相關內容《美國公債》就業數據向好 美國十年期債息先升後回<br />\n<br />\nWood管理5個交易所買賣基金(ETF)，集中於顛覆性創新企業，今年已得150億美元資金流入。旗艦基金Ark Innovation去年回報率近1.5倍，目前淨資產總值逾170億美元。(fc/da)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.1081227/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.1081227%2F2&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv6jPH3pfKCXBWMLigY0rPLs%3D&h=6747bda5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.1081227/2</a>"},{"pid":"955da2db6e513f2ca62934efeb9ac463fc21ab88","tid":2438958,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T01:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81169278f0f610b542295c4ddc8a92eee77526fd","tid":2438958,"uid":50889,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T01:44:11.000Z","msg":"「女股神」Cathie Wood 牛西變得更廣闊"},{"pid":"a3ed907aa5b0c703a5b7a2a61fa3e5653c53d93f","tid":2438958,"uid":237459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"81169278f0f610b542295c4ddc8a92eee77526fd","tid":2438958,"uid":50889,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T01:44:11.000Z","msg":"「女股神」Cathie Wood 牛西變得更廣闊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T01:45:22.000Z","msg":"佢塊閪就闊"},{"pid":"e7da90b918efb070df218ad67ea19fbc02d1a3ca","tid":2438958,"uid":71298,"like":0,